		<title>Technology’s Role In Differentiating Customer Experiences</title>
		<link>http://nxteramarketing.wordpress.com/2008/04/29/technology%e2%80%99s-role-in-differentiating-customer-experiences/</link>
		<comments>http://nxteramarketing.wordpress.com/2008/04/29/technology%e2%80%99s-role-in-differentiating-customer-experiences/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Tue, 29 Apr 2008 20:02:59 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Elana Anderson</dc:creator>
		
